agere.flf — the substrate's typed-triangle figlet font
designed 2026-05-31 by claude with operator rismay at session-close
named for the Latin verb *agere* (to act)
which roots the substrate's agent / agenda / agency triad
each letter built from typed-triangle vocabulary
the substrate's cause rendered as typography — typed-everything in ink
